Release Notes

The film follows the musician Molle aka Mollono.Bass and his colleagues in
their daily lives for the 3000Grad Festival and especially for electronic
music. From the pastures of Mecklenburg it comes across Germany, France and
the Netherlands, to one of the most imaginative and familiar music festivals
in Germany. There we expect the thrilling joy of celebrating together on a
shimmering summer weekend, captured in a feature-length documentary with
music, heart, and a dash of fishing tales.
